sources.title: Planet Outlaws (1939) BUCK ROGERS
sources.description:
Stars: Buster Crabbe, Constance Moore, Jackie Moran
Directors: Ford Beebe, Saul A. Goodkind

Buck Rogers, an American soldier suspended in time, wakes up to find himself in the futuristic world of the year 2500 where an evil villain and his gang of outlaws are trying to gain total control the the universe!

1939 Buck Rogers serial re-edited to feature film length and re-released for theatrical distribution in 1953.
